      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Federal offices, courts and post offices will be closed tomorrow for a national day of remembrance in honor of President Gerald R. Ford. Stock markets in New York will also be closed, but city and state government offices, courts and schools will be open.</p>
        <p>Alternate-side parking rules will be in effect.</p>
      </block>
